_sText: * If you have, or plan to use this map on a server please let me know! * Cs_Snowshot presented by: Crackshot Alright everyone this is my first hostage rescue map, its kind of small but doesn't seem that way when you play on it. its been in production for quite some time because I have been trying to work out some issues in the map but everything has come together nicely. if you find any problems with it please let me know! otherwise please enjoy the map. *Reminder:* Make sure to leave feedback on this submission and leave assessments if you enjoyed the map!
